---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Tarif Pengiriman
description: "Cek tarif pengiriman kargo Perdana Prima Express ke seluruh Indonesia. Ongkir dari Bandung, Jakarta, Surabaya ke Kalimantan, Sulawesi, Papua, Bali dan 200+ kota lainnya."
---

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-low px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <span class="font-label text-label-caps text-secondary mb-4 block tracking-[0.1em] uppercase">Jaringan Logistik Kepulauan</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-display-lg-mobile md:text-display-lg text-primary leading-tight mb-6">Cek Tarif Pengiriman</h1>
      <p class="font-body text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-8">
        Estimasi ongkir ke seluruh pelosok Nusantara — Jawa, Sumatra, Kalimantan, Sulawesi, hingga Papua. Hubungi kami via WhatsApp untuk tarif pasti dan negosiasi muatan besar.
      </p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/{{ site.wa.bandung.number }}?text={{ site.wa.bandung.text }}"
         class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-8 py-4 font-bold text-body-md inline-flex items-center gap-2 active:scale-95 transition-transform">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">chat</span>
        Tanya Tarif via WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-1/3 opacity-10 pointer-events-none hidden lg:block">
    <div class="w-full h-full bg-primary-container rounded-l-full transform translate-x-1/2"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Info Tarif -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">

      <!-- Cara Hitung -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline text-headline-md text-primary mb-8">Cara Perhitungan Tarif</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 text-primary shrink-0">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">straighten</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-1">Berat Aktual vs. Berat Volume</h4>
              <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Tarif dihitung berdasarkan berat yang lebih besar antara berat aktual (kg) dan berat volume.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 text-primary shrink-0">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">calculate</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-1">Rumus Berat Volume</h4>
              <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">(Panjang × Lebar × Tinggi dalam cm) ÷ 4.000 = Berat Volume (kg)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 text-primary shrink-0">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">route</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-1">Faktor Tujuan</h4>
              <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Tarif bervariasi tergantung kota tujuan, pulau, dan moda pengiriman yang dipilih (udara/laut/darat).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 text-primary shrink-0">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">info</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-1">Negosiasi Muatan Besar</h4>
              <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Untuk muatan di atas 50 kg atau pengiriman rutin, hubungi kami untuk tarif khusus yang lebih kompetitif.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Kontak Tarif -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 border border-outline-variant">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-headline-md text-primary mb-6">Tanya Tarif Langsung</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8">
          Hubungi cabang terdekat Anda untuk mendapatkan estimasi ongkir yang akurat dan penawaran terbaik.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          {% for branch in site.branches %}
          <div class="bg-surface p-5 border border-outline-variant">
            <p class="font-body text-body-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-1">{{ branch.city }}</p>
            <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-3">{{ branch.address }}</p>
            <a href="https://wa.me/{{ site.wa[branch.waKey].number }}?text={{ site.wa[branch.waKey].text }}"
               class="font-label text-label-caps text-primary flex items-center gap-2 hover:gap-4 transition-all">
              WA {{ site.wa[branch.waKey].label }} <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Tabel Tarif dari Bandung -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-low px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <span class="font-label text-label-caps text-secondary mb-2 block">REFERENSI TARIF</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-headline-md text-primary">Tarif Kirim dari Bandung</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-4">
        Tarif di bawah adalah estimasi. Tarif final dikonfirmasi saat pemesanan.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <a href="/tarif-kirim-dari-bandung/"
         class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-8 py-3 font-bold text-body-md inline-flex items-center gap-2 hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity mb-8">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">table_chart</span>
        Lihat Tabel Tarif Lengkap dari Bandung
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <a href="/tarif-kirim-asal-jakarta/"
         class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-primary text-primary px-8 py-3 font-bold text-body-md inline-flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">table_chart</span>
        Lihat Tabel Tarif dari Jakarta
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="bg-primary text-on-primary py-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="font-display text-display-lg-mobile mb-6">Butuh Tarif Lebih Murah?</h2>
    <p class="font-body text-body-lg text-on-primary-container mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Kami memberikan harga spesial untuk pengiriman rutin dan volume besar. Hubungi kami sekarang.
    </p>
    <a href="https://wa.me/{{ site.wa.bandung.number }}?text={{ site.wa.bandung.text }}"
       class="bg-surface text-primary px-12 py-4 font-bold text-body-md inline-flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined">chat</span>
      Negosiasi Tarif via WhatsApp
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
